
Dashboard UI & Reports Generation

Secure the system (protect routes, use prepared statements).

Admin: Full access (manage users & clients, sales, expenses, reports).

Manager: Manage sales & expenses, view reports.

Employee: Limited access (add/view sales & expenses, no report access).


